[b][u][size=24pt]Server Status[/size][/u]:[/b] [i][size=14pt]Online[/size][/i]
Hey guys. This is a brand new server I just started up a few days ago. I haven't got a chance to advertise it so I will now. This is basically TrisidiaX v3 source with some things changed/fixed.
Things changed to TrisidiaX: [code]-Changed home to Canafis. -Added ::rats and ::bunnies (Areas to kill rats/bunnies for rares) -Added mystery box. -Fixed a few minor glitches. Open to suggestions. -Still need to change some prices of items. Too lazy to.[/code]

Staff: Owner -Dan
Co-Owner -Drbooblicker
Admin -Marijuana
Mod -Devilgtx
Don't come on my server asking for staff because you won't get it.

One last thing, server is normally online 3:30 PM - 11:00/11:30 PM - US Central time (-6 GMT) on weekdays and whenever I wake up to whenever I got to sleep on weekends. I can't get a vps yet so yeah.
